OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother grey start with
OL,6,Ffurther rain across the north, which
OL,7,Fmay turn heavier and more persistent
OL,8,Flater. Some sunny spells developing
OL,9,Facross the south and feeling mild for
OL,10,Fall.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fmoving across the region on Thursday
OL,14,Fbefore turning brighter with some
OL,15,Fshowers on Friday. Further rain likely
OL,16,Flater on Saturday. Temperatures
OL,17,Freturning to nearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
